entities.description: A categorization of the country into specific geographical regions, such as New England, Middle Atlantic, etc.
A broader categorization of the country into regions such as North East, North Central, etc.
The raw, unadjusted count of cases within each category.
The percentage representation of cases within each category.

relationships.description: Indicates that a country is divided into multiple smaller divisions for survey purposes.
Indicates that a country is divided into broader regions for survey purposes.
Indicates the unweighted frequency count for each country division.
Indicates the percentage representation for each country division.
